I"3<p>With this sensor platform, you will be able to integrate the test build results reported by <a href="https://travis-ci.org/">Travis-CI</a> working within Home Assistant.</p>
<h2>Setup</h2>
<p>Create a GitHub <a href="https://github.com/settings/tokens">access token</a> with the following scopes:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>read:org</strong></li>
<li><strong>user:email</strong></li>
<li><strong>repo_deployment</strong></li>
<li><strong>repo:status</strong></li>
<li><strong>write:repo_hook</strong></li>
</ul>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable this platform, please add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
sensor:
  - platform: travisci
    api_key: YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
</code></pre>
<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
